{"tid":1386522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"就係因為某一班廢青廢老既存在 香港先會搞成咁","createTime":"2019-07-30T11:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T12:23:22.000Z","uid":137632,"like":223,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8ecc4d6a98df95d8c225d88bd6d423a099c02521","tid":1386522,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:07:43.000Z","msg":"真係不吐不快<br />\n香港個教育制度到底係出左咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令咁多撚屌唔敢出聲<br />\n有咩事都選擇<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沉默</span></span> 就係呢份沉默累死左好多人呀你知唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩都扮睇唔到扮唔知 事不關己就最好  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢種垃圾心態幾時先可以消失<br />\n<br />\n大學都就grad 點解身邊可以十個有九個都係港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家仲係度返大陸飲喜茶 有人比人打就話佢預左<br />\n我<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌晒你地老母</span></span>呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地爭取到既野你唔值得擁有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c7e09e63b825b5a8485803fe14e5fcbedad636","tid":1386522,"uid":137632,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:08:34.000Z","msg":"真係好撚嬲<br />\n竟然話唔駛理啦，我地讀得咁辛苦唔通出去摶拉咩<br />\n我屌 讀屎片架你?"},{"pid":"a7486e805080dc25138e26f0c69beef9426e1c0c","tid":1386522,"uid":137632,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:09:15.000Z","msg":"日撚日剩係識同條女扑野<br />\n兩隻港豬一鳩樣"},{"pid":"93e8c64dfb136059b20b47937832b1d6